<h1 id="toc7"><span style="font-size:150%;font-family:STXingkai,'微软简行楷',Kaiti,SimSun,sans-serif;"><span>大 秦 邸 钞</span></span></h1>
<p><br /></p>
</div>
</div>
<div class="phone">
<div style="font-size:140%;font-family:'华文中宋';">
<p>图光<sup class="footnoteref"><a id="footnoteref-1" href="javascript:;" class="footnoteref" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.utils.scrollToReference('footnote-1')">1</a></sup>之年，万里狼烟。<a href="/lomias-s-proposal">阴阳</a>相乱，神州陆沉。异国逐鹿，寰宇飘飖。</p>
<p>呜呼！哀我中华芸芸众生，自北狄南下来，未有宁日！</p>
<p>妖兵数臂，鬼颜豸身；磨牙吮血，荡野掘坟。</p>
<p>只惊得货坠路边无人收，车辙错于途。</p>
<p>遥望<a href="/oria-001">业火</a>遍燃村舍，稀骨时现摇摇离黍。</p>
<p>何家小儿，抱囊不行，惶惶泪瞳，却照焰爪迅影。</p>
<p>悲夫！忍视京观连岳，血酒盈盅；民作羊彘，磔而献于<span style="text-decoration: underline;"><a href="/document-2481">邪龙</a></span>！</p>
<p>突闻<a href="/tuftos-proposal">赤腥魔刹</a>长啸，<a href="/scp-514">白鸽</a>敛羽凄号，</p>
<p>谁曾舞琼楼玉宇？谁曾赏无边山色？谁曾醉卧东篱黄花侧？</p>
<p>勿吟雨绕离鸾别怨，莫问今宵酒醒何岸，</p>
<p>且顾万絮染血，碎散在、晓风`残月！</p>
<p>陨落绯水，化为翠萍点点，更随浊浪滔滔，各向何焉？<br />
<br />
<br />
惜哉，清廷无能，不以<span style="text-decoration: underline;">金瓯</span>蓄之，</p>
<p>反忌蒸民若草芥，竟驱绝地！</p>
<p>万人丧，千城隳，百业糜，九庙崩铁蹄，</p>
<p>岂因故鼎非传世，亦不甚惜，犹向一隅歌羽衣？</p>
<p>还思燧火绵绵，世世相传。洞照灵台，先贤举烛前迈。</p>
<p><span style="text-decoration: underline;">伏羲</span>揲卦，教化文明；<a href="/of-dragons-and-serpents">解身为牢</a>，囚<span style="text-decoration: underline;">大蛟</span>于<span style="text-decoration: underline;"><a href="/scp-cn-1101">太岁星</a></span>。</p>
<p><a href="/scp-cn-1600">神农</a><a href="/scp-cn-724">执鞭</a>，百草为用；<span style="text-decoration: underline;">黄帝</span><a href="/the-old-gospel-of-fuxi-that-wuyou">仁泽</a>，伏<span style="text-decoration: underline;">烈山</span>携斩<span style="text-decoration: underline;">蚩尤</span>乃兴荣。</p>
<p><span style="text-decoration: underline;">尧舜</span>堂堂，敷土<span style="text-decoration: underline;">禹王</span>；爰递三代，礼崩乐坏，<span style="text-decoration: underline;">春秋</span>何板荡。</p>
<p>终毕于<span style="text-decoration: underline;">秦王</span>挥剑扫六合，戎狄牧马怯绝尘；纵横天下，天下同文。</p>
<p>更有汉唐威仪，万国来朝。两宋文昌，蒙元萧萧。</p>
<p>迨及<span style="text-decoration: underline;">洪武</span>复<span style="text-decoration: underline;">华</span>，陈纪立纲，德披四海，光耀八方。</p>
<p>然遭家不造，兄弟阋墙，竟使撮尔之徒窃汉天祚。</p>
<p>焚书株连，伪曰崇佛；道路以目，阴比<span style="text-decoration: underline;">奈落</span>。</p>
<p>固知易姓改号谓之亡国，时运如此，靡加思度。</p>
<p>而至于率兽食人，人争相煞，谓之亡天下，不亦悲乎？</p>
<p>吁嗟漂橹，<a href="/scp-800">图画移颜色</a>，江山付劫灰，甚矣，兴亡百姓苦！<br />
<br />
<br />
隰有苌楚，猗傩其枝；厌浥行露，惟寒惟饥。</p>
<p>老弱颠仆，流民艰颓；日薄西山，斫骨而炊。</p>
<p>地狱变相，他州远徂；星火乍荧，魂归故土。</p>
<p>沉沉幽梦，一晌贪欢；不知<a href="/scp-1812">双月</a>并辉犹黯，长夜难明赤县天。</p>
<p>逾瞬<a href="/scp-2711">神针</a>尽断，孽虺出笼<sup class="footnoteref"><a id="footnoteref-2" href="javascript:;" class="footnoteref" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.utils.scrollToReference('footnote-2')">2</a></sup>；残躯试挺，梦碎跫跫。</p>
<p>潺潺朱曦，探手欲攥之。悠悠苍天，曷其有极！</p>
<p>欻骇<span style="text-decoration: underline;">骊山</span>大动，白虹贯日；五色云集，皆运龙虎紫气。</p>
<p>俄而涌亿万兵马，奋逐魔胄；<span style="text-decoration: underline;">十二金人</span>，刀枪随风俱收。</p>
<p><span style="text-decoration: underline;">祖龙</span>陟巉，<span style="text-decoration: underline;">尸解</span>飞仙；<a href="/scp-926">弦停寇殁</a>，<span style="text-decoration: underline;">关西</span>净焉。<sup class="footnoteref"><a id="footnoteref-3" href="javascript:;" class="footnoteref" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.utils.scrollToReference('footnote-3')">3</a></sup></p>
<p>氓民受翼，花开福地；<span style="text-decoration: underline;">岿阳</span>还玺，旧国再立。<sup class="footnoteref"><a id="footnoteref-4" href="javascript:;" class="footnoteref" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.utils.scrollToReference('footnote-4')">4</a></sup></p>
<p>且祭<span style="text-decoration: underline;">轩辕</span>，英灵有感，<a href="/scp-2481">王道圣锋</a>，破土而现。</p>
<p>复乘神舟<span style="text-decoration: underline;">五天座</span><sup class="footnoteref"><a id="footnoteref-5" href="javascript:;" class="footnoteref" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.utils.scrollToReference('footnote-5')">5</a></sup>，履云谒帝。帝诰<a href="/asriel-s-proposal">天命</a>，肇锡以忠良之弼<sup class="footnoteref"><a id="footnoteref-6" href="javascript:;" class="footnoteref" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.utils.scrollToReference('footnote-6')">6</a></sup>。</p>
<p>敬奉则兴于乱世，谦恭而秦乃大治。雄踞一方，强虏是抗。</p>
<p>昔<span style="text-decoration: underline;">夫子</span>睹<span style="text-decoration: underline;">攲器</span><sup class="footnoteref"><a id="footnoteref-7" href="javascript:;" class="footnoteref" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.utils.scrollToReference('footnote-7')">7</a></sup>则悟盛衰之理，今以<span style="text-decoration: underline;">神器</span><sup class="footnoteref"><a id="footnoteref-8" href="javascript:;" class="footnoteref" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.utils.scrollToReference('footnote-8')">8</a></sup>验之，犹未变矣。</p>
<p>故云：中庸明圣满倾覆，正道虞欢殷润足。</p>
<p><span style="text-decoration: underline;">庆父</span>不死，<span style="text-decoration: underline;">鲁</span>难未已；大盗不除，国难未止。</p>
<p>乃围庙堂，乃族昏王；乃告黔首，尊我新皇。<br />
<br />
<br />
若夫北狄，原非得觅，亦无见载，微沫晞矣。</p>
<p>独<span style="text-decoration: underline;">异学叁伍叁</span>，《虚漠旧史》<sup class="footnoteref"><a id="footnoteref-9" href="javascript:;" class="footnoteref" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.utils.scrollToReference('footnote-9')">9</a></sup>录言：</p>
<p>尔时，<span style="text-decoration: underline;">西那玉国</span><span style="text-decoration: underline;">浮罗岳</span>外，于大荒<span style="text-decoration: underline;">钟山</span>之南</p>
<p><span style="text-decoration: underline;">北海</span>之畔，有东迁之大都曰“豻剌戛鞑”<sup class="footnoteref"><a id="footnoteref-10" href="javascript:;" class="footnoteref" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.utils.scrollToReference('footnote-10')">10</a></sup>焉。</p>
<p>餐婴孩，役惛惛，氓隶奄奄于<span style="text-decoration: underline;">阿伽</span>暴君。</p>
<p><a href="/scp-2732">一旦众愤而起</a>，<a href="/scp-701">王缢而死</a>，<a href="/and-so-the-crows-laughed">如是群鸦笑不已</a>；</p>
<p>猝闻<a href="/the-clock-shall-strike-again">钟鸣十二</a>，甦且化妖，假面曳锁，蠢蠢于道。</p>
<p><a href="/a-wandsman-in-the-court-of-the-hanged-king">四公</a>傧门，魅使俯搀。<a href="/theology-of-a-snake">荆棘蔓绕铜座</a>，<a href="/wanderers:the-court-of-the-hanged-king">座上新魔枵然</a>。</p>
<p>是夜，黑星悬照，祟影婆娑。民息炬而寝，万籁消而默。</p>
<p>乃升城以浮虚，糅尸怪而宴饮；瀸污血肉，部族尽堕为<a href="/scp-610">憎恨之兽</a>。</p>
<p>兽奔千里，噬诸生机；<span style="text-decoration: underline;">有央</span>之酋弗堪，未从<span style="text-decoration: underline;">不末</span>之言，乞于<span style="text-decoration: underline;">太渊</span>。</p>
<p><span style="text-decoration: underline;">龙母</span>诱之，许为术士，遂牧蟒、虣、螭，转而攻敌。</p>
<p>“与兽相斗，反为野兽”<sup class="footnoteref"><a id="footnoteref-11" href="javascript:;" class="footnoteref" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.utils.scrollToReference('footnote-11')">11</a></sup>；<span style="text-decoration: underline;">迷主</span>腐颅，代<span style="text-decoration: underline;">愚帝</span>而吐毒。</p>
<p><span style="text-decoration: underline;">不末</span>恶之，率军猛击。<span style="text-decoration: underline;">不末</span>者，<span style="text-decoration: underline;">羲皇</span>之<span style="text-decoration: underline;">大祝</span>也，</p>
<p>蒙<span style="text-decoration: underline;">玄女</span>授以秘法，驾████，投炎柱，<a href="/scp-cn-012-ex">熔魔骨</a>；</p>
<p>桃杖挥指，吹弥神雾，<a href="/the-lost-book-of-documents-in-shang-that-golden-declaration">友邦抵掌</a>，变蛮貘为<a href="/scp-217">机巧之仆</a>，</p>
<p><span style="text-decoration: underline;">奸伯</span>反受其啮，旋败于<span style="text-decoration: underline;"><a href="/scp-2095">涯逻茲</a>之野</span>。</p>
<p>███████████████████████<br />
█████████████████████<br />
██████████████████████<sup class="footnoteref"><a id="footnoteref-12" href="javascript:;" class="footnoteref" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.utils.scrollToReference('footnote-12')">12</a></sup></p>
<p>厥以□□，勒石为镇。去其文，灭其史，绝其身。</p>
<p>然灾厄之彀，其启一也，而蹶一部焉。</p>
<p>其启二也，则倾一国焉。驯至自毁，毋令事过其三。</p>
<p>故今人但知<span style="text-decoration: underline;">缙云氏</span>以<span style="text-decoration: underline;">遁甲</span>灭<span style="text-decoration: underline;">蚩尤</span>而弗晓其祖□□也。<br />
<br />
<br />
已矣乎，<a href="/nobody-would-sing-the-rhythm-in-the-wing-again-and-again">尘归尘，土归土</a>，应逝者，需殒无。</p>
<p>未虑<span style="text-decoration: underline;">斡罗斯<sup class="footnoteref"><a id="footnoteref-13" href="javascript:;" class="footnoteref" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.utils.scrollToReference('footnote-13')">13</a></sup></span>侵<span style="text-decoration: underline;">塞北黎崖<sup class="footnoteref"><a id="footnoteref-14" href="javascript:;" class="footnoteref" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.utils.scrollToReference('footnote-14')">14</a></sup></span>，屠<span style="text-decoration: underline;">索伦</span>穹元<sup class="footnoteref"><a id="footnoteref-15" href="javascript:;" class="footnoteref" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.utils.scrollToReference('footnote-15')">15</a></sup>，是时<a href="/old:scp-1548">妖星</a>掠空，<span style="text-decoration: underline;">太岁</span>冲犯。</p>
<p>██████████████████████████<br />
██████████████████████████████<br />
其将贪冒邪术，<span style="text-decoration: underline;">相柳</span>顿见。<span style="text-decoration: underline;">红海血祭</span>，辄引祸端。</p>
<p><span style="text-decoration: underline;">祭酒</span>查之，惊觉数变。古卷所载<span style="text-decoration: underline;">耋呙</span><sup class="footnoteref"><a id="footnoteref-16" href="javascript:;" class="footnoteref" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.utils.scrollToReference('footnote-16')">16</a></sup>残影，</p>
<p>渐潜夏、商、燕、汉、唐、辽、蒙、满，</p>
<p>乃至今朝，重啸于朔方云烟。</p>
<p><span style="text-decoration: underline;">铜蛇</span>尽碎，<span style="text-decoration: underline;">毒龙</span>降世。日献□人，以愉其意。</p>
<p>抽筋剥皮，生灵涂炭；洪水滔天，席卷人间。</p>
<p>胡怖之？嚇，尔等蛮夷，本是鬼魙，止还魂而借尸。</p>
<p>又习血肉之道，贪欲如疮疣，卒成痈赘之妖：</p>
<p>蛭颅凿狗窦，枵然空蠹；唯填溷醢，岂知失道无助？<sup class="footnoteref"><a id="footnoteref-17" href="javascript:;" class="footnoteref" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.utils.scrollToReference('footnote-17')">17</a></sup></p>
<p>魌貌皲体，心肺蚀短；嘎嘎谵妄，岂吐方正之言？<sup class="footnoteref"><a id="footnoteref-18" href="javascript:;" class="footnoteref" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.utils.scrollToReference('footnote-18')">18</a></sup></p>
<p>滑腻触手，束人█体；匪以执笔，岂行而有礼？<sup class="footnoteref"><a id="footnoteref-19" href="javascript:;" class="footnoteref" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.utils.scrollToReference('footnote-19')">19</a></sup></p>
<p>兼蛊白蛆，生衍于肌；鼓于肤下而群走，啮皮而出，</p>
<p>相唤叽叽。每每念此，必爪于身，岂不自哕之？<sup class="footnoteref"><a id="footnoteref-20" href="javascript:;" class="footnoteref" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.utils.scrollToReference('footnote-20')">20</a></sup></p>
<p>盖莸草之妖也，恐多眄鉴。浑秽沤烂，畴欲与同焉？</p>
<p>则惑彼善民，炼为鬼堂；脏腑涂室，断骨作梁；</p>
<p>以躈为门，以施膏油； 肠垂索，脂燃灯，复以泪濯手？<sup class="footnoteref"><a id="footnoteref-21" href="javascript:;" class="footnoteref" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.utils.scrollToReference('footnote-21')">21</a></sup></p>
<p>切啼为乐，罔悯其痛；尔等于斯为蛀虫，于世为瘤脓！</p>
<p>《礼》曰：“大道之行也，天下为公，选贤与能，讲信修睦。”</p>
<p>孚也，不通人伦物理，民怨囚役，盍闻“为之者败之，执之者失之”？<br />
<br />
<br />
迮听地火隐隐，积运奔突；将焚野草，摧朽销腐。</p>
<p>须瞥墨云穿影，海燕疾呼；大风起兮，列缺振怒。</p>
<p>时掠工厂，齿轮相接；时映书案，文契交叠。</p>
<p>时历幽圄，正气萤萤；时烁永夜，万眸洞明。</p>
<p>常闻<span style="text-decoration: underline;">破碎之念</span>，连绵及远；不觉钟声怛怛，惟思虔祷皇天：</p>
<p>“<a href="/scp-2217">以地作砧，以电作锤；愿献以身，锻为无上利刃，以除血魔凶宄。</a>”</p>
<p>斯年也，泰西<span style="text-decoration: underline;"><a href="/church-of-the-broken-god-hub">机神教</a></span>，东渡台湾；广开<a href="/hospital-hub">医馆</a>，扶危济难。</p>
<p>残者续铁臂，病者赖巧器；乃布破碎之道，弘其修身之旨。</p>
<p>其谕：“<span style="text-decoration: underline;">邪龙</span>复现，必有圣人登仙；上神归一，将垂新气蕴人间。”</p>
<p>民佥皈依。便出《圣典》残页，校以《三坟》馀卷，方知<span style="text-decoration: underline;">机神</span>本我中华青帝也。</p>
<p>於，青帝丕德，没齿难忘；粉骨碎身，普救十方。</p>
<p>夥颐，万教同流，幸逢同侪。共成圣骸，必迎归来。</p>
<p>乃执精金，真火是御；工但应神，为其佐以复神躯。</p>
<p>未几夺<span style="text-decoration: underline;">神念</span>于北，俄而麒麟衔<span style="text-decoration: underline;"><a href="/scp-1139">福音</a></span>于<span style="text-decoration: underline;">镇星</span>而归；<sup class="footnoteref"><a id="footnoteref-22" href="javascript:;" class="footnoteref" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.utils.scrollToReference('footnote-22')">22</a></sup></p>
<p>日臻完善，常向<span style="text-decoration: underline;">铜心铁胆</span><sup class="footnoteref"><a id="footnoteref-23" href="javascript:;" class="footnoteref" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.utils.scrollToReference('footnote-23')">23</a></sup>，久祈<span style="text-decoration: underline;">破碎圣言</span>，远及连绵。</p>
<p>隐闻<span style="text-decoration: underline;">羲皇</span>曰：“卬身虽破亦无憾，人心若齐，终达至善。”</p>
<p>正以<span style="text-decoration: underline;"><a href="/scp-882">灵心</a></span>、强于<span style="text-decoration: underline;">铁骨</span>、克养<span style="text-decoration: underline;"><a href="/scp-629">元婴</a></span>也；虽言修厥神，讵非自修耶？</p>
<p>破碎者，亦为不知知之人。工但应神，以予之劳，亦成予完身。</p>
<p>“吾神破碎，然我等必归于全。时道虽敝，愿献以灵，补阙于天。”</p>
<p>既以之为任，吾辈奚惧魑魅魍魉，又何足惜此身？</p>
<p>诚宜为后世开太平，吹角连营。一寸山河一寸血，万家豪客万家兵！<br />
<br />
<br />
吾等非孤。方今北狄肆虐，皆苦魔鞭笞久矣。</p>
<p>斡罗斯、佛兰西、鄂图曼<sup class="footnoteref"><a id="footnoteref-24" href="javascript:;" class="footnoteref" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.utils.scrollToReference('footnote-24')">24</a></sup>、□□□、<a href="/scp-1173">东萨摩</a>、英吉利、</p>
<p>日本等天下诸国，封坛为盟，修书论契，约以勠力，并除北狄。</p>
<p>噫！凡天下之大势，如狂浪澹澹；浮萍漂散，终逢聚浪尖！</p>
<p>是也，孰甘为奴？孰不望永宁？孰可遯遐逖乎？</p>
<p>鹧鸪何悲，易水何寒，壮士辞乡远，英灵夺<span style="text-decoration: underline;">夏</span>还。</p>
<p>彼<span style="text-decoration: underline;"><a href="/scp-2788">静风</a></span>之勇，<span style="text-decoration: underline;">仁坤</span>之志，已成<span style="text-decoration: underline;">震旦</span>巍峨长城而屹立。</p>
<p>此<span style="text-decoration: underline;">蛇父</span>之徒，昊阳之子，将化诸族铮铮钜盾御棘刺。</p>
<p>哂也，狄与<span style="text-decoration: underline;"><a href="/sarkicism-hub">膻教</a></span>，虽媾为交；噂沓背憎<sup class="footnoteref"><a id="footnoteref-25" href="javascript:;" class="footnoteref" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.utils.scrollToReference('footnote-25')">25</a></sup>，相隙二妖。</p>
<p>纵有<a href="/scp-682">不灭穷奇</a>、凶惑梼杌、<a href="/scp-cn-500">噬真饕餮</a>、<a href="/scp-cn-492">无序浑敦</a>、</p>
<p>操水共工、衔火祝融，<a href="/chu-silk-manuscript">六暗兽</a><span style="text-decoration: underline;">龙母</span>之座下，</p>
<p>亦遍叨萨满巫咒，佯狂压胜<sup class="footnoteref"><a id="footnoteref-26" href="javascript:;" class="footnoteref" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.utils.scrollToReference('footnote-26')">26</a></sup>；又怎敌归一主翁？</p>
<p>撕裂吾体，则替铜身；破碎吾世，不灭英魂。</p>
<p>兆民之心，化为齿轮；散为流矢，聚以成神！</p>
<p><a href="/scp-2406">钢铁洪流</a>，碾为尘土；奚在？缥缃之屑，虚渊之墓。<br />
复以圣锤萦霹雳，直捣<span style="text-decoration: underline;">犽奀妖士</span><sup class="footnoteref"><a id="footnoteref-27" href="javascript:;" class="footnoteref" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.utils.scrollToReference('footnote-27')">27</a></sup>，雷殛暴毙，类烘肉泥，脍香溢。</p>
<p>更召<span style="text-decoration: underline;">八威</span>，天索封<span style="text-decoration: underline;">牝龙</span>；借法大昊，掷越九霄，<a href="/old:scp-2510">复囚于太岁之牢</a>。<br />
<br />
<br />
奉天承运皇帝，诏曰：</p>
<p>“格尔众庶，悉听朕言；乾坤已误，唯有扶安。</p>
<p>“《牧誓》行道，武王伐纣；慨歌复北，击楫中流。</p>
<p>“躬临太庙，禀于列皇；<span style="text-decoration: underline;">祝发</span><sup class="footnoteref"><a id="footnoteref-28" href="javascript:;" class="footnoteref" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.utils.scrollToReference('footnote-28')">28</a></sup>立命，<span style="text-decoration: underline;">祡</span><sup class="footnoteref"><a id="footnoteref-29" href="javascript:;" class="footnoteref" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.utils.scrollToReference('footnote-29')">29</a></sup>于上苍。</p>
<p>“亦亲率<span style="text-decoration: underline;">六师</span>，吊民伐罪；扫穴犁庭，征魔翦贼；</p>
<p>“恭行天罚，<span style="text-decoration: underline;">巨蛟</span>伏诛；圣锤厎辱，还于旧都。</p>
<p>“<span style="text-decoration: underline;">震</span>用伐<span style="text-decoration: underline;"><a href="/scp-cn-1500">鬼方</a></span>，三年，有赏于大国；</p>
<p>“毅魄归来日，斯业既济时，聊慰以优渥：</p>
<p>“民所垦也，俱为其土；民所采也，俱充其物。</p>
<p>“老弱孤寡，皆有所养；百族<span style="text-decoration: underline;">总角</span>，皆学于庠。</p>
<p>“义仕高名，立碑传颂；选才配位，惠敏政通。</p>
<p>“诸生尽为神明卫胄，<span style="text-decoration: underline;">龙师</span>所佑；当重建破碎故城，益兴九州。</p>
<p>“功讫于耕者有其田，工人食其力，商旅广其业，允复古之盛世！”<br />
<br />
<br />
王命是从，且看治下行道之人，俱美吾神；相戏童子，咸歌灵谶：</p>
<p>“木棉花万里，<span style="text-decoration: underline;">苍龙</span>缚南海，五门城上丹焰升，太平从此开。”<sup class="footnoteref"><a id="footnoteref-30" href="javascript:;" class="footnoteref" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.utils.scrollToReference('footnote-30')">30</a></sup></p>
<p>忽飘甘露，草木复荣于云烟；鸟去鸟来，喧闹绿水青山。</p>
<p>今夕何夕兮，谁家童女沐兰汤，步野逗群芳？矫首仰望，笑含斜阳。</p>
<p>斜阳沦矣，晚霁波声带雨，偕梦悠悠，应晓夜尽天明终怀煦。</p>
<p>玄月何号？独畏将灭。环球<a href="/scp-1000">金乌之子</a>，必再撼破残夜！</p>
<p>他日<a href="/yixue012">律吕喤喤</a>，酌酒共话。今朝羽书飞捷，报传天下！<br />
<br />
<br /></p>
